^5Help - Broadcast
~5USAGE: .broadcast [^5message~5]
~5WHERE: ^5message ~5is the text you wish to broadcast
 
~5Use this command when you want to send an anonymous message to all the 
~5users currently online.  This is ideally used for emergency 
~5situations, and shutting down notices.  To review the last several
~5broadcasts, do not supply a ^5message~5.
 
~5SEE ALSO
  ^5.help shout

